fields.description: The date on which devices in the deployment start receiving the update. When not set, the deployment starts as soon as devices are assigned. The Timestamp type represents date and time information using ISO 8601 format and is always in UTC time. For example, midnight UTC on Jan 1, 2014 is 2014-01-01T00:00:00Z.
